data.description:
Welcome to  this beautiful and modern home centrally located in Lantana. This house features  4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2 living areas for flexible arrangements. Ceramic tiles throughout the house. Security is paramount, boasting a wireless ADT system, sensors on every window, and exterior cameras for comprehensive surveillance. An automated sprinkler system conserves water, a 20x10 storage space caters to belongings, and a dedicated side entrance accommodates recreational vehicles. Energy efficiency includes a tankless gas water heater, LG washer-dryer set, and a kitchen with luxurious KitchenAid PRO appliances. Central air conditioning with a Nest thermostat ensures optimal climate control throughout the residence Discover the epitome of modern living in this captivating residence located at 1434 West Hardee Street, Lantana, FL 33462. Boasting a harmonious blend of elegance and functionality, this home offers a spacious layout with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2 distinct living areas for versatile living arrangements.

Security is paramount, featuring a cutting-edge wireless ADT security system with sensors meticulously placed on every window, motion detectors, and smoke sensors, ensuring peace of mind for you and your loved ones. Moreover, comprehensive surveillance is maintained with strategically positioned exterior security cameras.

Enhancing both convenience and conservation, the property incorporates an automated sprinkler system fed by a well, ensuring lush landscaping while efficiently managing water usage. A sizable 20x10 storage facility caters to your organizational needs, providing ample space for all your belongings.

The property's functionality extends outdoors with a dedicated side entrance perfect for accommodating trailers, RVs, or boats, offering added convenience for your recreational pursuits.

Enjoy the perks of energy-efficient utilities with a tankless gas water heater, providing an uninterrupted supply of hot water while optimizing energy consumption. A premium LG gas washer and dryer set add further convenience to daily living.

The kitchen stands as the heart of this home, boasting luxury stainless steel KitchenAid PRO appliances that elevate culinary experiences. The thoughtful integration of a central air conditioning system coupled with a Nest thermostat ensures optimal climate control throughout the home.

Step into the outdoor sanctuarya meticulously designed patio area featuring a BBQ space, deck, and fireplace, ideal for hosting gatherings or unwinding in the comfort of your private oasis.

Nestled in a desirable location, this home seamlessly combines luxurious amenities with functionality, promising a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication. Don't miss this opportunity to make 1434 West Hardee Street your new addressa place where modern convenience meets timeless elegance.
